snippet.title: Dead Wells Opening Story Cinematic
snippet.description:
Took a long time to put together but here is the opening cinematic explaining  the short but to the point story of Dead Wells. If your interested in the game please Wish List it on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2525660/Dead_Wells_The_Devil_Fragment/

Music: Irrational Rain by Koi-Discovery
